rows.label: tlk47200161_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Whew! I'm taking a break
from fetching water.

rows.label: tlk47200161_01_msg0002
rows.name:
My house is further up, so
it's a right pain to have to
lug the buckets uphill...

rows.label: tlk47200161_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Auntie Correl gets water on tap
in her kitchen, doesn't she?
Some of us have it easy...
